4|title=Kongou Falls, Gabon \u2013 World Waterfall Database|website=www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-16}}</ref>\n|-\n! 15\n| [[Kootenai Falls]]\n| [[File:Kootenai Falls 2019-07-13.jpg|100px]]\n| {{sort|00731|731}}\n| 9\n| 258\n| [[Kootenay River|Kootenay]]\n| {{flag|United States}}\n| {{coord|48.4555015|-115.763198|format=dms|name=Kootenai Falls}}\n| \n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com/waterfall/Kootenai-Falls-120|title=Kootenai Falls, Montana, United States \u2013 World Waterfall Database|website=www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-16}}</ref>\n|-\n! 16\n| [[Kaieteur Falls]]\n| [[File:GuyanaKaieteurFalls2004.jpg|100px]]\n| {{sort|00663|663}}\n| 226\n| 113\n| [[Potaro River|Potaro]]\n| {{flag|Guyana}}\n| {{coord|5.17497870|-59.4804760|format=dms|name=Kaieteur Falls}}\n| \n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com/waterfall/Kaieteur-Falls-114|title=Kaieteur Falls, Guyana \u2013 World Waterfall Database|website=www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-16}}</ref>\n|-\n! 17\n| [[Rheinfall]]\n| [[File:Rheinfall. Img 3.jpg|100px]]\n| {{sort|00595|595}}\n| 24\n| 122\n| [[Rhein River|Rhein]]\n| {{flag|Switzerland}}\n| {{coord|47.677640|8.615512|format=dms|name=Rheinfall}}\n| Largest waterfall in [[Europe]] by average flow rate.\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com/waterfall/Rheinfall-115|title=Rheinfall, Switzerland \u2013 World Waterfall Database|website=www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com|language=en|access-date=2020-01-16}}</ref>\n|-\n! 18\n| [[Kalandula Falls]]\n| [[File:Kalandula waterfalls of the Lucala-River in Malange, Angola (2).JPG|100px]]\n| {{sort|00566|566}}\n| 105\n| 411\n| [[Lucala River|Lucala]]\n| {{flag|Angola}}\n| {{coord|-9.073885|16.000709|format=dms|name=Kalandula Falls}}\n| \n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.worldwaterfalldatabase.com/waterfall/Kalandula-Falls-453|title=Kalandula Falls, Angola \u2013 World Wa